# gdlint config for the demo + addon GDScript. We relax three style rules that clash with this
# project's conventions and keep the semantic checks (unused-argument, expression-not-assigned,
# duplicated-load, function-arguments-number, name checks, …) that catch real problems:
#   - max-line-length: some lines (e.g. manifest strings) are intentionally very long.
#   - class-definitions-order: definition order here is deliberate, not gdlint's.
#   - constant-name: private const collections use the `_lower` convention (e.g. `_tabs`).
disable:
  - max-line-length
  - class-definitions-order
  - constant-name
